      have h_one_neq: 1 ≠ n_k A := by sorry
```

The proof attempts to show that `eval (↑q) (phi n)` divides the sum `∑ A, (q ^ n - 1) / (q ^ n_k A - 1)`. It uses `Finset.dvd_sum` to prove that the divisibility holds for each term in the sum. For each term, it tries to show that `q ^ n_k A - 1` divides `q ^ n - 1`.

